Other song choice model

ml.Repeatr4_os.Rd

This model was estimated on only the data for the other songs of each show, that is all the songs after the first song.

ml.Repeatr4_os

Format

An object of class mlogit of length 17.

Details

The utility formula was as follows:

choice ~ choice ~ choice ~ yearsold_1 + yearsold_2 + yearsold_3 + yearsold_4 + yearsold_5 + yearsold_6 + yearsold_7 + yearsold_8 + song2 + ... + song92
